                        <h2>Moles</h2>
                        <h4>Moles</h4>
                        <p>We`re molis, it`s something more that a common clan, we`re family</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about" id="about">
                <div class="about__title">
                    <div class="about__title-line"></div>
                    <h1>Our History</h1>
                    <div class="about__title-line"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-wrapper">
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <h4>History</h4>
                        <p>Our friends' server has already seen six exciting seasons, and now we're eagerly awaiting the seventh! Each season brings new events that unite us in fun adventures. We celebrate victories and support each other in tough times. Communication is key, let's make even more amazing moments together!</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="about-img">
                        <img src="img/about-img.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>

            </section>

            <section class="info" id="info">
                <div class="info__title">
                    <div class="info__title-line"></div>
                    <h1>Information</h1>
                    <div class="info__title-line"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-wrapper">
                    <div class="info-text">
                        <h2>Wanna join us?</h2>
                        <p>How to find out if you`re suitable for us?</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>You like being in friends group</li>
                            <li>You`re going to build something more than dicks</li>
                            <li>You won`t live us in a week</li>
                            <li>You really appreciate admin`s work</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>If you are, applicate the form and just wait!</p>
                    </div>

                    <form action="/sending/email" class="info-form" method="post">
                        <h3>Application <span>form</span></h3>
                        <input type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder="enter your name...">
                        <input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="enter your email...">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn">Send</button>
                        {{#if message}}
                        <p class="warning">{{message}}</p>
                        {{/if}}
                    </form>
                </div>
            </section>

            <a href="#logo" class="tothetop"><i class='bx bx-chevron-up'></i></a>
        </div>
    </main>

